{"tid":1526482,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[轉貼] 機場仲未夠塞喔！！！","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:59:42.000Z","uid":61520,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e0389b0cf13cbf5e259eef451c59ed82a6f5d3e5","tid":1526482,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屋企人有Pass入機場，佢話重未夠人塞到落唔到車！ 咁樣點癱瘓機場？重有巴士的士阿</span>"},{"pid":"46beb4a754f786f5053effdc8523e6b42532859e","tid":1526482,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"[突發] 警察惡行 請retweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n當年有份聯署既人，大部分都走哂，仲留得係度既人，你都估到佢係咩人？？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人性嘅，應該一早 劈炮，唔再做 cctvb吧！但係佢仲要做足7年，做到2019 年今日，然後佢想洗白拎光環，叫3毛 錢7開post造勢，想拎光環夾橫行直入海關警察入境. 繼續染紅政府為藍屍發聲。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我心裡梗係想佢係因良心發現而辭職啦<br />\n佢係鬼良心發現辭職咩<br />\n係<em>比</em>班同事投訴佢番工唔做野掛住化妝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">覺得比人杯先辭渣<br />\n仲帶哂光環咁<br />\n屋企警察世家攞咩光環<br />\n<br />\n最後 cctvb假新聞記者主播無一個無辜 <br />\n唔好亂信任何消息 為佢哋洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警 主播 死 全 家</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef007194b50c22bbd296aeca566411e2d52aa9c4","tid":1526482,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場要人！ ！ ！ 屋企人有Pass入機場，佢話重未夠人塞到落唔到車！ 咁樣點癱瘓機場？重有巴士的士入！</span><br />\nthx for 開post！ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場要人！</span>"},{"pid":"6d7328a7363377c02f8f9e09aea0cadad50097b8","tid":1526482,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FtNRGCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtNRGCU.jpg&h=e9b7c03f&s={SIZE}\" />"}